('AI Web Research Assistant', 'Productivity', 'Researches any topic across the web and returns structured, sourced summaries in seconds. Knowledge workers spend 19% of time searching for information; AI compresses to near-zero.', '$5k–$30k MRR', '1M+/mo', '$4.2B', 82, 46, 89, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['productivity','research','AI','web']),
('PDF & Document Chat Tool', 'Productivity', 'Chat with any PDF, report, or contract to extract answers without reading it. Lawyers, researchers, and consultants read 100+ pages daily; AI Q&A compresses to 5 minutes.', '$5k–$30k MRR', '800k+/mo', '$3.8B', 82, 48, 88, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['productivity','PDF','AI','documents']),
('AI Competitive Analysis Builder', 'Productivity', 'Automatically generates competitor teardowns from a URL input with positioning and SWOT. Founders spend 10+ hours on competitive analysis before each board deck; AI completes in 10 minutes.', '$6k–$40k MRR', '200k+/mo', '$3.5B', 80, 40, 90, 'Rising', true, ARRAY['productivity','competitive-analysis','AI','strategy']),
('Personal AI Knowledge Graph', 'Productivity', 'Connects notes, bookmarks, emails, and documents into a queryable personal knowledge base. Roam Research has 200k power users; AI-automated linking removes the manual tagging barrier.', '$4k–$24k MRR', '500k+/mo', '$3.2B', 78, 44, 87, 'Rising', true, ARRAY['productivity','knowledge-graph','AI','notes']),

