('Smart Scheduling Link Tool', 'Productivity', 'Context-aware scheduling that proposes optimal times based on energy, timezone, and meeting type. Calendly has $3B valuation; AI-native scheduling that optimizes for cognitive performance is the next.', '$4k–$24k MRR', '1M+/mo', '$3.5B', 78, 52, 86, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['productivity','scheduling','AI','calendar']),
('Time Tracking & Billing AI', 'Productivity', 'Passive AI time tracker that categorizes work automatically without manual timers. Toggl has 5M users; 40% of billable hours go untracked in professional services; AI captures the gap.', '$4k–$24k MRR', '600k+/mo', '$3.2B', 76, 48, 86, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['productivity','time-tracking','billing','AI']),
