('AI SOP Generator & Documenter', 'Productivity', 'Watches how work is done and generates standard operating procedures automatically. Businesses spend $46B/yr on process documentation; AI generation from screen recording is 100x faster.', '$6k–$40k MRR', '100k+/mo', '$4.5B', 80, 36, 91, 'Explosive', true, ARRAY['productivity','SOPs','documentation','AI']),
('Browser AI Co-pilot Extension', 'Productivity', 'Lives in the browser to summarize pages, draft emails, fill forms, and answer questions in context. Arc Browser has 1M users; AI co-pilot layer for any website is the power user differentiator.', '$4k–$24k MRR', '3M+/mo', '$4.8B', 84, 48, 90, 'Explosive', false, ARRAY['productivity','browser','AI','extension']),
('AI Clipboard & Snippets Manager', 'Productivity', 'Intelligent clipboard that learns frequently pasted content, tags it, and surfaces it contextually. TextExpander has 100k users; AI that learns your patterns without manual setup is the leap.', '$3k–$18k MRR', '800k+/mo', '$2.2B', 74, 44, 84, 'Rising', true, ARRAY['productivity','clipboard','snippets','AI']),
('AI Form & Data Entry Automator', 'Productivity', 'Fills web forms and repetitive data entry tasks from a personal data profile automatically. Workers spend 4.5 hours/week on data entry; AI automation reclaims that time immediately.', '$4k–$24k MRR', '500k+/mo', '$3.5B', 78, 42, 88, 'Rising', true, ARRAY['productivity','automation','forms','AI']),

